data.description: Motivated Seller! Let's make a deal!!! Welcome to this STUNNING home situated in a quiet cul-de-sac, featuring 4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths. This like new home less than 1 years old, offers ample sunlight, an open floor plan with a two-story great room, beautiful upgraded finishes, and features a pristine  kitchen. The kitchen boasts a gas range, calacatta quartz countertops, multi-height wall cabinets and a spacious layout open to the family room.  A pocket door leads to an office nook and a large pantry for all your food storage. You will find a beautiful 1/2 bath located on the main level tucked away for your guests. The lower living space/flex room provides extra room for relaxation or entertainment. Upstairs, you will find the luxurious owner's retreat with an en suite bath, complete with a large shower & walk-in closet.  A few steps up lead to the remaining three spacious bedrooms, each with ample storage and closet space, along with a second full bath and a second story convenient laundry room. The unfinished basement offers additional space for a rec room, man cave, bar, or home gym. Plumbing is available for a full bath, adding versatility to this fantastic home.  Enjoy spending time outside on the covered front porch or relax on the back patio. Conveniently located close to shopping, interstates, WBAFB (Area B:15-20 mins & 22 mins to area A). Don't miss the opportunity to make this modern and well-appointed home your own!
